profile:
Welcome to Budget Blinds of SW Saskatchewan. We proudly serve Moose Jaw, Saskatoon, Swift Current, Kindersley, and all surrounding rural areas with FREE In-Home Consultations & NO MILEAGE FEES.

Moose Jaw: 306-690-7850
Saskatoon: 306-242-5706
Swift Current: 306-773-7851
Kindersley: 306-463-0850

We're your local experts and are proud to be backed by the #1 provider of custom window coverings in North America that has provided design-driven solutions for over 25 years. With the highest levels of customer satisfaction, you'll have the peace of mind and security that comes with choosing the proven leader. We’ll get to know you and your unique style so we can deliver the perfect solution for your home. 

***

Explore what Beautiful can do for your windows. Contact us today to schedule your appointment. We’re looking forward to working with you.
products: Window coverings; blinds; shutters; shades; drapes; wood & faux wood shades; honeycomb/ cellular shades; roller shades; solar shades; custom cornices & valances; dual shades; roman shades & more.
services: Free In-Home Consultations, no mileage fee; quoting in the home, professional measuring & installation services.
brands: Signature Series (Springs Window Fashions); Englightened Styles; Mera; ODL;
memberships: Saskatoon & Region Home Builders' Association; Moose Jaw Chamber of Commerce
warranty_terms: The most competitive manufacturer warranties PLUS a 5-year No Questions Asked warranty on almost all products.
